title: Baked and stuffed acorn squash
ingredients: ['2 tablespoons dark brown soft sugar', '1 tablespoon melted butter', '2 large acorn squash, halved and seeded', '2 tablespoons olive oil', '2 cloves garlic, chopped', '2 sticks celery, chopped', '2 carrots, chopped', '240g tinned chickpeas, drained', '80g raisins', '1 1/2 tablespoons ground cumin', 'salt and pepper to taste', '400ml chicken stock', '175g couscous']
